        <profile name="Special Issue Ammunition" typeId="ccb3-7790-3139-7975" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="88cf-44bf-3e16-f7d8">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="e24a-6018-20cf-d76c">Each time a Sternguard veteran squad fires, the controlling player can choose which type of ammunition is being used. Each special ammunition replaces the boltgun profile (including combi-weapons). All models in the squad must use the same ammunition type during that shooting phase.</characteristic>
